name: Temporal-Tie-Strength-Group-Based-Routing-Scheme
description: This repository contains the code for the TS-GBR scheme, which improves message delivery in mobile opportunistic networks by forming node groups based on temporal-tie strength. The scheme enhances delivery rates and reduces overhead, as shown using SLAW, TVCM, and NCCU trace data.
